                                            The headquarters of Thompson Creek Mining Co, a miscellaneous nonmetallic minerals, except fuels company, are located at Clayton, ID. It boasts an annual revenue of $19.5 million and employs 96 people. Without a doubt, you'll be unable to deny the appeal of Thompson Creek Mining Co. A CEO heads up the firm.
                                        









